Contact Us

Have a question about your medication or need assistance? We're always here to help, feel free to contact us online or by phone.

[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row column_structure="3_5,2_5" _builder_version="4.9.4" _module_preset="default" global_colors_info="{}"][et_pb_column type="3_5" _builder_version="4.9.4" _module_preset="default" global_colors_info="{}"][et_pb_text _builder_version="4.9.7" _module_preset="default" text_font="Poppins||||||||" global_colors_info="{}"]

Get help by phone

For any questions related to your medications, account issues, or prescription notification preferences, please contact us at 928-485-4315

Visit us on Social Media

We are available on social media. Stay updated with news and events from our pharmacy. Be sure to like our Facebook and Instagram pages.  

Contact us online

Need to contact us via e-mail? Fill out the form below and we will contact you. Please allow 24-48 hours for a response. For more quicker responses please call us directly.
